revision.text:
{{also|Yawn}}
==English==
{{wikipedia}}
[[Image:Yawning kitten.ogv|thumb|right|A kitten yawning.]]
===Etymology===
Partly from {{inh|en|enm|yanen}}, {{m|enm|yonen}}, {{m|enm|yenen|t=to yawn}}, from {{inh|en|ang|ġinian|t=to yawn, gape}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*ginōną|t=to yawn}}; and partly from {{inh|en|enm|gonen|t=to gape, yawn}}, from {{inh|en|ang|gānian|t=to yawn, gape}}, from {{inh|en|gem-pro|*gainōną|t=to yawn, gape}}; both from {{der|en|ine-pro|*ǵʰi-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*ǵʰeyh₁-|t=to yawn, gape}}. Cognate with {{cog|frr|jåne|t=to yawn}}, {{cog|stq|jaanje}}, {{m|stq|joanje|t=to yawn}}, {{cog|dum|genen}}, {{m|dum|ghenen|t=to yawn}}, {{cog|nds-de|jahnen|t=to yawn}}, {{cog|de|gähnen|t=to yawn, gape}}, dialectal {{cog|sv|gana|t=to gape, gawk}}, dialectal {{cog|no|gina|t=to gape}}.
Compare also {{cog|cu|зѣѭ}} ({{cog|ru|зи́нуть}}, {{m|ru|зия́ть}}), Greek {{m|grc|χαίνω}}), Latin {{m|la|hiō}}, {{cog|xto|śew}}, {{cog|txb|kāyā}}, {{cog|lt|žioti}}, Sanskrit {{m|sa|जेह्}}
===Pronunciation===
